Interface StreamServiceGrpc.AsyncService

StreamServiceGrpc.StreamServiceImplBase
Enclosing class:
StreamServiceGrpc
public static interface StreamServiceGrpc.AsyncService
 A StreamService is used to coordinate with a WebRTC the listing,
 addition, and removal of registered video streams.
